{"tid":1834776,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港政府幾時用緊急法推返「蒙面法」?","createTime":"2020-01-22T14:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T15:01:01.000Z","uid":199727,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"65802fd3e01171aab76beafd6d5a8b1cea0cdb3a","tid":1834776,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"面對疫情持續擴散，22日晚上武漢市更宣佈實施「緊急禁蒙法」。市政府發佈通告，武漢公共場所實施佩戴口罩，各公共場所經營者應當要求進入其場所的顧客佩戴口罩後方可進入其經營的公共場所，並在場所入口處設置醒目、清晰的佩戴口罩的提示；對未佩戴口罩進入場所者應當予以勸阻，對不聽勸阻的人員，由各相關主管部門按照各自職責依法處理。構成違反治安管理行為的，由公安機關依法予以處罰；構成犯罪的，依法追究刑事責任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】增至17死 緊急推蒙面法 出街不戴口罩者將送官究治<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200122&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60509574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200122%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60509574&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzQEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=b9a18e52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200122%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60509574&h=045d98b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200122&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60509574</a>"},{"pid":"0e1f43998d501f95f0e4b8dfe87a1ddd12f8b8d8","tid":1834776,"uid":186074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:30:00.000Z","msg":"支持蒙面法   支那狗落香港唔戴直接遣返"},{"pid":"8665414802f5424e4c9817a88ba0d0d670ccdf11","tid":1834776,"uid":206003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:30:41.000Z","msg":"支持蒙面法"},{"pid":"280f97f8163b778057730c83d7c4c253d40925f4","tid":1834776,"uid":199727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:31:28.000Z","msg":"武漢當局帶頭造反"},{"pid":"67d21843a70540c970ac4d8b00971a2568df8a56","tid":1834776,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"藍屍點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56538b07a574a60972b29dd7c39345568ad61737","tid